      "manualSections": [
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-tooltip — on a real trigger element",
          "html": "  <p>The tooltip <em>behavior</em> attaches via <code>x-tooltip</code> to a real trigger element (button, span, …) — not a standalone custom tag.</p>\n  <wb-demo columns=\"4\">\n    <wb-button id=\"btn-top\" x-tooltip=\"Tooltip text\" position=\"top\">Top</wb-button>\n    <wb-button id=\"btn-bottom\" x-tooltip=\"Tooltip text\" position=\"bottom\">Bottom</wb-button>\n    <wb-button id=\"btn-left\" x-tooltip=\"Tooltip text\" position=\"left\">Left</wb-button>\n    <wb-button id=\"btn-right\" x-tooltip=\"Tooltip text\" position=\"right\">Right</wb-button>\n  </wb-demo>"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-progressbar — attribute-based progress bar",
          "html": "  <p>Apply directly to any element, no custom tag required — an alternative to <code>&lt;wb-progress&gt;</code> above.</p>\n  <wb-demo>\n    <div x-progressbar value=\"40\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 24px;\"></div>\n  </wb-demo>\n  <wb-demo>\n    <div x-progressbar value=\"80\" variant=\"success\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 24px;\"></div>\n  </wb-demo>"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-notify — one-off notification",
          "html": "  <wb-demo>\n    <button x-notify message=\"New notification received\" class=\"wb-button\">Show Notify</button>\n  </wb-demo>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "forms",
      "title": "Form Controls",
      "description": "Buttons, inputs, selects, checkboxes, switches, textareas",
      "icon": "📝",
      "components": [
        "button",
        "checkbox",
        "input",
        "search",
        "select",
        "switch",
        "textarea",
        "slider",
        "toggle"
      ],
      "manualSections": [
        {
          "heading": "🧩 wb-button + x-* behavior composition",
          "html": "  <p class=\"wb-note\">Any <code>x-*</code> behavior (ripple, tooltip, toast, etc.) composes onto a button the same way it does onto any other element — stack as many as you want, in any order, with no wrapper components.</p>\n  <style>\n    .wb-behaviors { list-style: none; margin: 1rem 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }\n    .wb-behaviors li { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.75rem; }\n    .wb-behavior-tag { display: inline-block; padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; background: var(--bg-secondary); color: var(--info-color); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); white-space: nowrap; }\n    .wb-behavior-desc { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; }\n  </style>\n  <p class=\"wb-note\">Each <code>x-</code> attribute adds one capability to the button — no JavaScript.</p>\n  <wb-demo columns=\"3\">\n    <wb-button variant=\"primary\" x-ripple>Ripple</wb-button>\n    <wb-button variant=\"secondary\" x-tooltip=\"Helpful hint\" position=\"top\">Tooltip</wb-button>\n    <wb-button variant=\"success\" x-toast message=\"Saved!\" toast-variant=\"success\">Toast on click</wb-button>\n    <wb-button variant=\"info\" x-copy copy-text=\"Copied from a wb-button!\">Copy to clipboard</wb-button>\n    <wb-button variant=\"warning\" x-wobble>Wobble</wb-button>\n    <wb-button variant=\"ghost\" x-tada>Tada</wb-button>\n  </wb-demo>\n  <ul class=\"wb-behaviors\">\n    <li><span class=\"wb-behavior-tag\">x-ripple</span><span class=\"wb-behavior-desc\">material-style ripple on click</span></li>\n    <li><span class=\"wb-behavior-tag\">x-tooltip</span><span class=\"wb-behavior-desc\">hover hint, positionable</span></li>\n    <li><span class=\"wb-behavior-tag\">x-toast</span><span class=\"wb-behavior-desc\">fires a toast notification</span></li>\n    <li><span class=\"wb-behavior-tag\">x-copy</span><span class=\"wb-behavior-desc\">copies text to the clipboard</span></li>\n    <li><span class=\"wb-behavior-tag\">x-wobble</span><span class=\"wb-behavior-desc\">wobble animation</span></li>\n    <li><span class=\"wb-behavior-tag\">x-tada</span><span class=\"wb-behavior-desc\">tada celebration animation</span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p class=\"wb-note\">Stack multiple <code>x-</code> attributes on one button — they layer, they don't conflict.</p>\n  <wb-demo columns=\"1\">\n    <wb-button variant=\"primary\" x-ripple x-tooltip=\"Ripple + tooltip + toast\" position=\"top\" x-toast message=\"Saved!\" toast-variant=\"success\">Save (ripple + tooltip + toast)</wb-button>\n    <wb-button variant=\"error\" x-ripple x-wobble x-toast message=\"Deleted\" toast-variant=\"error\">Delete (ripple + wobble + toast)</wb-button>\n    <wb-button variant=\"info\" x-copy copy-text=\"npm i wb-starter\" x-tooltip=\"Click to copy the install command\" position=\"bottom\" x-ripple>Copy install cmd</wb-button>\n  </wb-demo>"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-fieldset — collapsible fieldset",
          "html": "  <wb-demo>\n    <fieldset x-fieldset>\n      <legend>Personal Info</legend>\n      <label>Name: <input type=\"text\"></label>\n      <label>Email: <input type=\"email\"></label>\n    </fieldset>\n  </wb-demo>\n  <wb-demo>\n    <fieldset x-fieldset collapsible>\n      <legend>Advanced Settings (collapsible)</legend>\n      <label>API Key: <input type=\"text\"></label>\n    </fieldset>\n  </wb-demo>"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-form — ajax/validate behavior",
          "html": "  <wb-demo>\n    <form x-form>\n      <label>Username: <input type=\"text\"></label><br>\n      <label>Password: <input type=\"password\"></label><br>\n      <button type=\"submit\">Submit</button>\n    </form>\n  </wb-demo>"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-help — permanent hint text",
          "html": "  <p><code>x-help</code> is for hint text a user should see <strong>without hovering or interacting</strong> — a short instruction that sits permanently under a field (\"must be 8+ characters\"). If the text should only appear on hover/focus, use <code>x-tooltip</code> instead — the two are deliberately kept separate.</p>\n  <wb-demo>\n    <label>API Key: <input type=\"text\"></label>\n    <span x-help>Find this in your account settings under \"Developer\".</span>\n  </wb-demo>"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-label — including RTL layouts",
          "html": "  <wb-demo>\n    <input x-label=\"Label for input:\" type=\"text\">\n  </wb-demo>\n  <p>RTL layouts (Hebrew, Arabic) via <code>label-position=\"right\"</code>:</p>\n  <wb-demo>\n    <input x-label=\"שם מלא\" label-position=\"right\" dir=\"rtl\" type=\"text\">\n  </wb-demo>\n  <div id=\"label-schema-validation\"></div>",
          "script": "    import Ajv from 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/ajv@8.12.0/+esm';\n    const schemaUrl = '../../src/wb-models/label.schema.json';\n    const ajv = new Ajv({ strict: false });\n    fetch(schemaUrl).then(r => r.json()).then(schema => {\n      const data = { required: false, optional: false };\n      let msg;\n      try {\n        const valid = ajv.validate(schema, data);\n        msg = valid ? 'Schema validation: PASS' : 'Schema validation: FAIL\\n' + JSON.stringify(ajv.errors, null, 2);\n      } catch (e) {\n        msg = 'Schema validation skipped (unresolved $ref): ' + e.message;\n      }\n      const out = document.createElement('pre');\n      out.style.background = '#222';\n      out.style.color = '#fff';\n      out.style.padding = '0.5em';\n      out.textContent = msg;\n      document.getElementById('label-schema-validation').appendChild(out);\n    });"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🧩 x-autosize — textarea that grows with content",
          "html": "  <wb-demo>\n    <textarea x-autosize style=\"width: 100%; min-height: 2rem;\">Type here and watch me grow!</textarea>\n  </wb-demo>"
        },
        {
          "heading": "🎨 Native Semantic Elements — x-* on plain HTML",
          "id": "native-semantic-forms",
          "html": "<p id=\"semanticsforms-p-13\">Enhanced form controls using standard HTML elements with <code id=\"semanticsforms-code-14\">x-*</code> behaviors.</p>\r\n\r\n  <!-- BUTTONS -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-15\">Button <code id=\"semanticsforms-code-16\">&lt;button&gt;</code></h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-17\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <button variant=\"primary\">Primary</button>\r\n      <button variant=\"secondary\">Secondary</button>\r\n      <button variant=\"success\">Success</button>\r\n      <button variant=\"danger\">Danger</button>\r\n      <button variant=\"warning\">Warning</button>\r\n      <button variant=\"ghost\">Ghost</button>\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <button variant=\"primary\" size=\"sm\">Small</button>\r\n      <button variant=\"primary\" size=\"md\">Medium</button>\r\n      <button variant=\"primary\" size=\"lg\">Large</button>\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n\r\n    <p>The <code>loading</code>/<code>icon</code>/<code>icon-position</code> attributes only work on the <code>&lt;wb-button&gt;</code> custom tag — a native <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> only maps <code>size</code>/<code>variant</code> to styling classes.</p>\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <wb-button variant=\"primary\" loading>Loading</wb-button>\r\n      <wb-button variant=\"secondary\" icon=\"💾\">Save</wb-button>\r\n      <wb-button variant=\"danger\" icon=\"🗑️\" icon-position=\"right\">Delete</wb-button>\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- INPUTS -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-33\">Input <code id=\"semanticsforms-code-34\">&lt;input&gt;</code></h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-35\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-36\" class=\"demo-grid\">\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-37\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-38\">Standard Input</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Type something...\">\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-40\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-41\">With Prefix/Suffix — needs <code>x-behavior=\"input\"</code>; there's no native auto-inject mapping for plain <code>&lt;input&gt;</code></label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"text\"\r\n            x-behavior=\"input\"\r\n            prefix=\"👤\"\r\n            suffix=\"@gmail.com\"\r\n            placeholder=\"Username\">\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-43\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-44\">Clearable</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"text\"\r\n            x-behavior=\"input\"\r\n            clearable\r\n            placeholder=\"Search...\">\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-46\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-47\">Validation States</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"text\"\r\n            x-behavior=\"input\"\r\n            variant=\"success\"\r\n            value=\"Valid Input\">\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"text\"\r\n            x-behavior=\"input\"\r\n            variant=\"error\"\r\n            value=\"Invalid Input\">\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- TEXTAREA -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-51\">Textarea <code id=\"semanticsforms-code-52\">&lt;textarea&gt;</code></h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-53\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-54\" class=\"demo-grid\">\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-55\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-56\">Auto-sizing</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <textarea autosize placeholder=\"Type to expand...\"></textarea>\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-58\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-59\">Character Count (Max 100)</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <textarea\r\n            show-count\r\n            max-length=\"100\"\r\n            placeholder=\"Limited bio...\"></textarea>\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- CHECKBOX & RADIO -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-61\">Checkbox & Radio</h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-62\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <p>checkbox has no <code>label</code> attribute of its own — wrap it in a real <code>&lt;label&gt;</code>.</p>\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <label><input type=\"checkbox\"> Accept Terms</label>\r\n      <label><input type=\"checkbox\" checked> Subscribe</label>\r\n      <label><input type=\"checkbox\" indeterminate> Indeterminate</label>\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <input\r\n        type=\"radio\"\r\n        name=\"plan\"\r\n        value=\"free\"\r\n        label=\"Free Plan\">\r\n      <input\r\n        type=\"radio\"\r\n        name=\"plan\"\r\n        value=\"pro\"\r\n        checked\r\n        label=\"Pro Plan\">\r\n      <input\r\n        type=\"radio\"\r\n        name=\"plan\"\r\n        value=\"ent\"\r\n        label=\"Enterprise\">\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- SWITCH -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-71\">Switch</h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-72\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <p><strong>Known gap (#322):</strong> <code>&lt;wb-switch&gt;</code> needs its schema built before it can render — that never happens on this page's runtime (<code>wb-lazy.js</code>, used by every standalone demo page), so it won't render here yet. This markup is the correct API; it works today on the main site (<code>?page=behaviors</code>).</p>\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <wb-switch label=\"Notifications\"></wb-switch>\r\n      <wb-switch label=\"Dark Mode\" checked></wb-switch>\r\n      <wb-switch label=\"Disabled\" disabled></wb-switch>\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- RATING -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-77\">Rating</h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-78\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <p><code>icon</code> takes a literal emoji character, not a keyword — <code>icon=\"heart\"</code> renders the literal text \"heart\", not ❤️. <code>precision</code> isn't a real attribute (not read anywhere in rating.js).</p>\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <wb-rating value=\"3\" max=\"5\"></wb-rating>\r\n      <wb-rating value=\"4.5\" max=\"5\" color=\"gold\"></wb-rating>\r\n      <wb-rating value=\"2\" max=\"10\" icon=\"❤️\"></wb-rating>\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- SELECT -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-83\">Select <code id=\"semanticsforms-code-84\">&lt;select&gt;</code></h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-85\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-86\" class=\"demo-grid\">\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-87\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-88\">Standard Select</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <select>\r\n            <option>Option 1</option>\r\n            <option>Option 2</option>\r\n            <option>Option 3</option>\r\n          </select>\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-93\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-94\">Searchable — <code>x-autocomplete</code>, not a <code>searchable</code> attribute on <code>&lt;select&gt;</code> (which doesn't exist)</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"text\"\r\n            x-autocomplete\r\n            items=\"Apple,Banana,Cherry,Date,Elderberry\"\r\n            placeholder=\"Search fruit...\">\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- RANGE -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-101\">Range <code id=\"semanticsforms-code-102\">&lt;input type=\"range\"&gt;</code></h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-103\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-104\" class=\"demo-grid\">\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-105\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-106\">With Value Display</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"range\"\r\n            show-value\r\n            min=\"0\"\r\n            max=\"100\"\r\n            value=\"50\">\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-108\">\r\n        <label id=\"semanticsforms-label-109\">With Labels & Suffix</label>\r\n        <wb-demo>\r\n          <input\r\n            type=\"range\"\r\n            show-value\r\n            show-labels\r\n            value-suffix=\"%\"\r\n            min=\"0\"\r\n            max=\"100\"\r\n            value=\"75\">\r\n        </wb-demo>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <!-- FORM -->\r\n  <h2 id=\"semanticsforms-h2-111\">Form <code id=\"semanticsforms-code-112\">&lt;form&gt;</code></h2>\r\n  <div id=\"semanticsforms-div-113\" class=\"demo-section\">\r\n    <p><code>x-form</code> has no <code>loading-text</code> option (that only exists in an unregistered alternate implementation).</p>\r\n    <wb-demo>\r\n      <form x-form ajax action=\"#\">\r\n        <div style=\"display: grid; gap: 1rem; max-width: 400px;\">\r\n          <input name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Name\" required>\r\n          <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Email\" required>\r\n          <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Message\" required></textarea>\r\n          <button type=\"submit\" variant=\"primary\">Send Message</button>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </form>\r\n    </wb-demo>\r\n  </div>"
        }
      ]
    },
